data.description: **$1,500 decorating allowance to buyer with acceptable offer**Welcome to this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the highly desired Windtree community! Step inside to discover a beautifully designed interior featuring modern finishes and a spacious floor plan. The generous living area is perfect for relaxation and entertaining, while the updated kitchen boasts sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage space. Right off the kitchen enjoy the large dining room with ample natural lighting!  Retreat to the tranquil primary bedroom, complete with an en-suite bathroom for added privacy. Two additional bedrooms round out this home. Outside, a large deck beckons for outdoor gatherings and BBQ's overlooking the lush backyard. This home offers easy access to Fort Liberty, shopping, dining, and entertainment options just steps away! Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously updated gem your own!
